                    <span>This is one of three texts I tried recently, seeking to learn Swahili. This one is okay if you just want to learn a few phrases for a short visit, but is poorly organized for actually learning the language. Unfortunately, the best text I found is now out of print, so you may be stuck with this unless you can haunt the second hand shops in Dar es Salaam or Z'bar.</span>
                  
              
